creator: Manas Maity
descriptionHtml:
Anima Foundation an Organization working for development of skill and empowerment of rural area of Bengal as well as India. Registered Under Govt of India , MSME and Govt of West Bengal.

Anima Foundation working for Development of Education , Digital Education , Education System , Online Assessment , EDP Training , Online Training , Website and Mobile App Development etc.

We provide support to rural area training institute to update there Class Room Management , Content , Online Assessment and Training support.

We also working in Govt Skill Project .

We help Startup in different way.

We also provide counselling and staffing solution service , try to provide job to our students.

When a person skilled and employable and begins earning, the journey of empowerment continues beyond the present generation.
